*tesseract-2.00 (30 Jul 2007)

  30 Jul 2007; Patrick McLean <chutzpah@gentoo.org> +tesseract-2.00.ebuild:
  Version bump, make tiff dependency optional and add LINGUAS for downloading
  extra language data.

